    units: 5, division: "upper",
    prereqs: [],
    ge: null, quarters: ["W"],
    desc: "Examines the relationship between language and gender. Topics include: gender differences in speech; linguistic gender norms and stereotypes; gender and the construction of identity in discourse; sexuality and language; sexism in language; social, educational, and political implications. (Formerly Languages 112.)",
