    prereqs: [],
    ge: null, quarters: ["F", "W", "S"],
    desc: "Examines the ways artists engage, interact, and comment upon ecology and nature in their artworks by examining environmental art from the 1960s through the present. Offers students a foundational introduction to art and artists working in the field of environmental and ecological art/activism.",
