    units: 5, division: "lower",
    prereqs: [],
    ge: "MF", quarters: ["F", "W", "S"],
    desc: "Methods of proof, number systems, binomial and geometric sums. Sequences, limits, continuity, and the definite integral. The derivatives of the elementary functions, the fundamental theorem of calculus, and the main theorems of differential calculus.",
