    units: 2, division: "lower",
    prereqs: [],
    ge: null, quarters: ["F", "W", "S"],
    desc: "Explores the philosophy of film through the viewing and discussionof several philosophically interesting films. Examines both the aesthetics of film and a variety of philosophical issues that particular films raise.",
