    prereqs: [["PSYC 100"]],
    ge: null, quarters: ["F", "W", "S"],
    desc: "Provides an overview of the social and cultural psychological study of immigrants in the United States. Examines the migration/immigration process; immigrants' social identities; schooling of immigrant youth; and impact of policy on the well-being of immigrants. Satisfies the senior seminar requirement. Satisfies the senior comprehensive requirement.",
