    ge: null, quarters: ["S"],
    desc: "Covers conversion of planned digital justice projects into a fundable grant proposal for social justice, integration of social activism, entrepreneurship and justice, and implementation of project. Topics include: funders, proposal design, field methods, project assessment, innovative digital technology applications, action research methods, project implementation. (Formerly Project Implementation and Grant Writing for Social Entrepreneurs.)",
    section: ["FREE"], rmpScore: 0
