    ge: null, quarters: ["S"],
    desc: "Involves students in a research project that combines advanced molecular methods with classical microbiological ones to investigate a topic of interest in the field of microbiology. Students learn to formulate hypotheses, identify and follow protocols, and interpret results. This course requires familiarity with basic microbiological concepts and techniques.",
    section: ["FREE"], rmpScore: 0
