    desc: "One-half hour of individual instrumental or vocal instruction. Repertory, technique, and performance practice. A minimum of six hours per week of individual practice is required. Concurrent enrollment in an ensemble in the lesson instrument or voice is required. Students are billed a course fee of $350. Admission by audition with the instructor prior to first class meeting. Enrollment priority given to music majors and minors.",
