    prereqs: [],
    ge: "CC", quarters: ["F", "W", "S"],
    desc: "A survey course in the musics of South Asia, covering classical, folk, and popular traditions. Consideration is given to the historical development of various musical and socio-musical genres, the social functions of the music throughout history, and instrumental and vocal forms with an emphasis on listening.",
