    ge: "CC", quarters: ["F", "W", "S"],
    desc: "Survey of the diverse and rich musical traditions of Jewish music in the diaspora from biblical times to the present. Examines the historical, social, and anthropological aspects of the different communities from sacred music through art and popular songs.",
