    desc: "Introduces students to the art of DJing. Becoming a skilled DJ requires many things: a deep love of music, the ability to read one’s audience, technical skill, and knowledge of DJ cultures and their histories. Students learn to DJ using both vinyl and digital formats, as well as how to organize events centered around dance music.",
